            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1653387606763-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your<strong> salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and roughly shred</p><p>Top, tail, peel, then grate your<strong> carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onions</strong> finely</p><p>Add the<strong> salad</strong>, <strong>grated carrot</strong> and<strong> sliced spring onion</strong> to a large mixing bowl</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1653387609487-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
