            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>peanut butter</strong> and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span><strong> boiled water</strong> in a small bowl and mix well until you have a smooth paste</p><p>Add your <strong>soy sauce</strong>, <strong>toasted sesame oil</strong>,<strong> rice vinegar</strong>,<strong> remaining chopped chilli</strong> (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> and mix well to combine – this is your <strong>peanut dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1653387620201-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
