            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1653387620201-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, drain your<strong> king prawns</strong>, then add them to the pan</p><p>Sprinkle your <strong>five-spice mix</strong> over the king prawns and cook for 4-5 min or until the prawns are cooked through – these are your <strong>bang bang king prawns</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1653387624052-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1653387624052-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1653387624052-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1653387624052-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1653387624052-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, fluff the <strong>cooked rice</strong> with a fork and add it to the <strong>crunchy salad</strong> – this is your <strong>crunchy rice salad</strong></p><p>Toss the <strong>crunchy rice salad</strong> in a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1653387627898-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1653387627898-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1653387627898-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1653387627898-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1653387627898-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> bang bang king prawns</strong> over the <strong>crunchy rice salad </strong>and drizzle the <strong>peanut dressing</strong> all over</p><p>Garnish with a sprinkling of <strong>toasted</strong> <strong>sesame seeds</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
